  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to determine the safety of lofexidine in the treatment of opiate
      withdrawal. Preliminary data will also be obtained to assess the ability of lofexidine to
      alleviate opiate withdrawal signs and symptoms.
    </textblock>
